I"9<h3 id="the-problem-with-dropdowns">The problem with Dropdowns</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Accessibility
    <ul>
      <li>A dropdown needs to be selected via keyboard and mouse. On top of that it should support any accessibility devices</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Appearance
    <ul>
      <li>The plain dropdown might not go with the rest of the design system</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

